{"title":"四害余生四海逃","authors":["郭沫若","华君武"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"四害余生四海逃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若诗　华君武画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1、苍蝇逃向英国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远从中国逃来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是十分愉快。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在此建立王国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传之子孙万代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中文虽叫苍蝇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英文是叫“福来”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可见英国绅士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表示忠诚拥戴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英国害过中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欠下鸦片旧债。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍蝇帮助霍乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也曾为过大害。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民憎恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是理所应该。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英国绅士欢迎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是同类相爱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）Fly的音译"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2、麻雀逃向美国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们真是自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到了北部美洲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦克、艾克、杰克，个个都是朋友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要吃就有粮吃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要游就可园游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃成便便大腹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散步华尔街头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人说超额利润，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着血的腥臭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有奶便是亲娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血腥于我何有？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十九亿美援，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有些政府领受。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比起某位总统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麻雀不算下流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3、蚊子逃向日本"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚊子虽然微藐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本领却是不小。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你英雄好汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都可把他病倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疟疾、脑炎、黄热，千村万落人少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就是瘟神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结队成群乱搞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国不准再呆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今逃往三岛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三岛岸姓政府，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不打中国交道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镇压日本人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专向美帝投靠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们同气相求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸血总要吸饱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4、老鼠逃向西德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老鼠别号高客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惯在梁上横行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传播鼠疫细菌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛烈不亚战争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两次世界大战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是德国兴兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今西部德国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣钵犹然继承。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人有战争贩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼠是瘟疫大神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自然同声相应，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不辞远道投奔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西德如果不收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝一定欢迎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄能识英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惺惺惯惜惺惺。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}